VLE 2.0.0
=========

**VLE2** is a tiny library designed to quickly develop DEVS, DTSS, DSDE and
multicomponent simulator.

See <http://www.vle-project.org/vle-Z.0> for introductory docs.

Gauthier Quesnel <gauthier.quesnel@toulouse.inra.fr>


Requirements
------------

Must have:

- c++ compiler (gcc or clang with C++11)
- libc++ or libstdc++
- boost (1.49 or better)

Compiling and installing
------------------------

Do this as root:

    ./configure --prefix=/usr --sysdir=/etc
    make
    sudo make install

Unless you are installing in your users directories:

    ./configure --prefix=$HOME
    make
    make install
